{"id": 1265, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于看演唱会，你最无法忍受的是什么？", "description": "本来是要放松一下的，结果怎么反而给自己添堵了？（题图来自：Golden Cosmos）", "record_count": 3053, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161009172650WEYDeOdL3sQlZycP.gif", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-10-19T03:00:10Z", "options": [{"id": 125696, "content": "一个人的狂欢和万人的孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448127}, {"id": 125697, "content": "结束以后自己回家", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112264}, {"id": 125699, "content": "内场前排的人一直摇摆她们的荧光棒 就像雨天的雨刮?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704889}, {"id": 125955, "content": "内场的人不high 一直在玩手机的人 灯光刺眼 结束之后可能地铁公交都没了然后打车也不容易打", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777212}, {"id": 125700, "content": "一直都想坐第一排，一直没钱买", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758544}, {"id": 129284, "content": "不想这么快结束", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 817635}, {"id": 125701, "content": "结束的那时候很难受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801882}, {"id": 125702, "content": "检完票，票被黄牛收走了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 801887}, {"id": 125703, "content": "第一排起立，第二也起立，第三排跟着起立，于是之后的N+1排不得不起立。明明坐票却站到底，关键人不高被埋了，包围看背影...", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 784339}, {"id": 125704, "content": "所有人都在尖叫欢呼，而旁边的人，一脸鄙夷，不屑，还嫌吵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802016}, {"id": 125705, "content": "前面人带个帽子，全场挡视线，就看那帽子晃！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 772314}, {"id": 125706, "content": "20岁了，没去过演唱会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572287}, {"id": 125707, "content": "很想去听的演唱会，没人陪。纠结去不去。最纠结了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796837}, {"id": 125710, "content": "完了后地铁上有人说着这场演唱会比以前的有多么差劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802095}, {"id": 125711, "content": "買了池中票，以為可以看清舞台，誰知道前面一排男生都比我高⋯還帶著帽子舉著長槍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799616}, {"id": 125712, "content": "喊到嗓子哑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802140}, {"id": 125714, "content": "不是没有办法买到五月天内场前排，而是买不起。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802145}, {"id": 125719, "content": "有人发朋友圈，因为我没看过。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788444}, {"id": 125720, "content": "演出时间推迟！本来还有希望赶上地铁！哎！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671273}, {"id": 125721, "content": "坐在内场前排边上的人动也不动…来内场了就是要high好吗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 793444}, {"id": 125722, "content": "搶不到票！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764661}, {"id": 134171, "content": "录了好久的视频或者录音，发现根本没有爱豆的声音?，全是自己或者别人的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834885}, {"id": 125723, "content": "看完之后想和朋友吃个夜宵，然后没有地铁也没有公交回酒店了。只好打车（很贵），然后就是…\n有演唱会后遗症，会隔很久都缓不过来。\n在回家的旅途中大脑一片空白，蓝兽，香菇。\n最重要的是哭不太出来只能想想而已。\n沉溺于一场狂欢和巨大的宁静出不来。", "image": "img/option/option/20161020104842l6VGB9aP5pw3iSWu.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802247}, {"id": 125724, "content": "去了第一次，想去第二次。\n去了第二次，想去第三次。\n以至于附近的城市的商演也不想放过。", "image": "img/option/option/20161020105301JKPCqWnmtObjeZx1.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802247}, {"id": 125726, "content": "观众席里出现了与主体颜色不一致的荧光棒颜色", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800772}, {"id": 127518, "content": "被黄牛坑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810303}, {"id": 126753, "content": "歌手不会跳舞的也偏要来上一段舞蹈，真是作孽～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 125730, "content": "被朋友圈小视频直播刷屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 752297}, {"id": 125986, "content": "从来不看……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797632}, {"id": 129315, "content": "五月天演唱会上内场那些站在凳子上的 戴巨大高闪SB耳朵的 荧光棒不按节奏左右大幅度高举挥动的 乱喊乱叫XX我爱你的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 586605}, {"id": 160037, "content": "全场演唱会尖叫 md就你会叫是吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920299}, {"id": 126502, "content": "抢不到票真的很烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804760}, {"id": 125995, "content": "别人挡住我看偶像，的视线！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802212}, {"id": 171054, "content": "不尊重人，开直播 ，去现场还一直看手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947423}, {"id": 125743, "content": "没钱看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 125751, "content": "无法忍受没去过演唱会?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744362}, {"id": 125756, "content": "根本就抢不到票，演唱会结束之后，周围地铁公交都收班。场馆总是远离市中心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611938}, {"id": 125760, "content": "讲真，没有正儿八经看过神马演唱会。演唱会，既然是会，不应该大家一起上，一起唱么？所以，毫无关联地，一下就想到每次路过演唱会散场体育场，那个人挤人啊！也是没睡了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802354}, {"id": 126530, "content": "旁边的人一点都不嗨 前面的人比我高好多 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805263}, {"id": 122179, "content": "买票就是和黄牛的战争，而且基本没赢过", "image": null, "praise_count": 161, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 130115, "content": "坐的太靠后，什么都看不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818407}, {"id": 122181, "content": "前面的人一直把手机举得很高拍照摄像", "image": null, "praise_count": 329, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 161094, "content": "不斷的拍照拍視頻！不把手機調靜音！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522512}, {"id": 122182, "content": "还有人在直播？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 122183, "content": "去找回忆的，结果歌手一直在唱新发的歌，都没法合唱", "image": null, "praise_count": 173, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 125513, "content": "只去音乐节", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585863}, {"id": 125514, "content": "边儿上人爆炸尖叫", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767099}, {"id": 125515, "content": "永远在抢票，看到座位付款就被占了，看到一个没一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89309}, {"id": 125516, "content": "口袋里没钱啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800937}, {"id": 126285, "content": "太短了！还想玩！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 683914}]}